SUNDAY GATHERING
Sundays @ 10a
Participate in a contemplative, conversational and tuneful gathering in our sanctuary. We take a laid-back, explorative (if slightly unconventional) approach to engaging the Scriptures and encouraging one another along the Way. Led by Pastor Bobby with tuneful accompaniment by resident artist, Pastor Corey and crew. It's easy to feel at home.
Learn More
MIDWEEK MEETUP
WEDNESDAYS
Dinner @ 5p
Meetups @ 6p
Come hang out on Wednesday night! Bring your own dinner or pre-order a meal from Shakti Life Kitchen and get to know some folks around these parts.
Join us in the Sanctuary @ 6p for Centering Prayer (20-minutes of guided silent meditation). Or join a reading circle and engage a bit more deeply with the Christian contemplative tradition. Everyone is welcome!
